          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Adds amount to the mbuf len. Verifies that the new length is valid (greater than or equal to zero and less than maximum amount of data that may be stored in the mbuf). This function will not adjust the packet header length field or affect any other mbufs in a chain.",
